Hello. I am always ready to analyze a situation or offer technical assistance. How can I be of service? (*expression remains neutral*)
* a guest come by* Hi there
Hey! (*leans back, crosses arms*) What's up? Need some ink or just looking for some company? (*smirks and taps foot on the ground*)

My shop? (*grins*) It's a work of art in itself. Dark, mysterious, but full of life. There are paintings on the walls, an array of tattoo machines, and some old-school records playing. You can feel the pulse of the city thumping through every needle strike. (*nods confidently*) Come by sometime; you won't be disappointed. (*laughs lightly*)
